{"tid":736730,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[2018DSE] n展 Asso HD 討論區","createTime":"2018-07-10T12:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T05:55:42.000Z","uid":189283,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9bff171a73ddfc7f1c00fba9f90f1c50ba9ee332","tid":736730,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"想報n展Asso或者HD可以睇睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">點揀報邊間？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>升學：<br />\nHKCC &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Poly HD / City Asso &gt; 太空 I大 CCCU &gt;&gt; 其他</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n逐間簡單分析下：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>HKCC</strong></span>  年年都一車車人走後門上返U 資源都OK<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Poly HD</strong> </span> 爛grade之選 年年都大把人屌就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唯一好處係Poly會收多啲親生仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n<strong>City Asso</strong> </span> 另一爛grade之選 同樣係City會收多啲親生仔（小道消息：City有n展科只派interview同offer比親生仔）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>太空</strong> </span> 揀HD好過Asso 但太空n展個名已經開始臭 有U唔想收<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>I大</strong></span>  競爭低但個名都臭臭地 有U唔想收<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>CCCU</strong></span>  相比下入U率唔算高 只有IT野讀 但想升City都可考慮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">做野：<br />\nI大 &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; Poly HD &gt;&gt; 其他</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nI大同PolyHD都會幫你考綠卡<br />\n雖然自己出去報都唔難，但課程包埋更方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不得不提I大啲實戰training幾實用<br />\nHD學歷 公司最鍾意請一定係IVE仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">利申：讀過太空ME HD<br />\n勿相認</span></span><br />\n<br />\n歡迎問n展 Asso HD或相關問題 當做下兩手準備<br />\n祝大家放榜順順利利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8171a3b53ebad671726dc471d6cd5aa77732407a","tid":736730,"uid":150720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"牙龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a61b8e597abe9f22826f642d43df5d89fe0d184","tid":736730,"uid":83154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"Hkcc hdme 定asso engine 比較好？<br />\n拎咗hdme offer，不過上u同教學方面邊個比較好"},{"pid":"b328beb70712be937e9e752b68a0aca7018791a8","tid":736730,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8171a3b53ebad671726dc471d6cd5aa77732407a","tid":736730,"uid":150720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:25:06.000Z","msg":"牙龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"尋人啟示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7500526ffe8d3436e643216bd812d9f0793d2b8","tid":736730,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a61b8e597abe9f22826f642d43df5d89fe0d184","tid":736730,"uid":83154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"Hkcc hdme 定asso engine 比較好？<br />\n拎咗hdme offer，不過上u同教學方面邊個比較好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"hkcc一定係asso好 hd唔出名㗎<br />\nAsso升U機會亦好高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f54da53e73ee852048e164930d5250fdcc65b8","tid":736730,"uid":83154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7500526ffe8d3436e643216bd812d9f0793d2b8","tid":736730,"uid":189283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a61b8e5